<center><h2><b>How to get started on this site?</b></h2></center>
<form class="well form-inline">	
In order to register for an event, you need to create a username. This will require an email account and it does use a validation email system.
<br /><img src="/img/username.png">
<br /> This will allow you to get our eblasts that contain the information for the next event.
<p>Next, when you are ready, click the register button on the front page of the website</p>
<img src="img/register.png">
This will start you through the event registration process.
<img src="img/registration.png">
<br />Once you get here, select the username you wish to pay for and it will auto fill the opposite dropdown.
<br />Add as many usernames as you would like to pay for and click PAY NOW
<img src="img/paynow.png">
<br />This will walk you throw the paypal process and when completed, it will redirect you back to the map.
<img src="img/mappage.png">
<br />Once you LEFT CLICK a seat, it will pop up a window and ask if you are interested in tournaments.
<br />If you don't want to sign up for a tournament, click close, otherwise click the picture and it will take you to the tournament page.
<br />Once the tournament page loads, signup - this will redirect you to another website where you can sign up yourself and/or your team for the associated tournament.
You should recieve an email with a barcode.
<br />Either print this off or use your smart phone to check into the event when you show up.
<br />If you don't remember or can't pull up the barcode, no worries - just use your normal username and password.





